txt.en: High in the cliffs above Helegrod, the traitorous Storvâgûn has pledged the giants of the Misty Mountains to the service of Angmar in exchange for vast riches.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when you leave the instance.</rgb>
Only the mightiest heroes can defeat Thrâng at his full strength. Are you up for the challenge?
You have returned to the high cliffs above Helegrod to face Storvâgûn.
You have defeated Thrâng and his Ghâshfra at their full strength! For your efforts, you will be rewarded!
